Class Controller

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.ctrl.Controller
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CommandHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RequestController, TransferController

    public abstract class Controller
extends java.lang.Object
implements CommandHandler
    Controller Handles requests from a command line interface and spawns transfers
